citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 8:54 am on
28-AUG-19.
Arrived at the facility the front gate locked. Contacted registrant by phone. Registrant was out of the town and did
not have another responsible person to accompany on an inspection.
